  <fr:mainmatter>
  <fr:p>For every morphism <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[P \to  F]]></fr:tex>, there is a unique way to extend the map to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[P^+]]></fr:tex> using the <fr:link href="algm-001F.xml" title="Sheaf" addr="algm-001F" type="local">sheaf condition</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F]]></fr:tex>. A section of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[P^+]]></fr:tex> consists of a matching family <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s_f]]></fr:tex>, and it is also the gluing of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\eta _P(s_f)]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
</fr:mainmatter>
